{
  "info": {
    "name": "Desafio Pitang Reembolsos",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "## Setup\n\n```bash\nbunx --bun prisma migrate reset --force\nbun run prisma:seed\nbun run dev\n```\n\n## Seed Users\n\n| Role | Email | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| ADMIN | admin@example.com | admin123 |\n| EMPLOYEE | employee@test.com | secret123 |\n| MANAGER | manager@test.com | secret123 |\n| FINANCE | finance@test.com | secret123 |\n\n## Variables\n\n| Variable | Source |\n|----------|--------|\n| `url` | http://localhost:3000 |\n| `adminToken` | Login (Admin) auto-save |\n| `employeeToken` | Login (Employee) auto-save |\n| `managerToken` | Login (Manager) auto-save |\n| `financeToken` | Login (Finance) auto-save |\n| `categoryId` | Copy from Create Category response |\n| `reimbursementId` | Copy from Create Reimbursement response |\n\n## Flow\n\n**Admin setup:** Auth login → Categories create → Users list\n**Full cycle:** Employee creates → submits → Manager approves → Finance pays\n"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "description": "Login for each role. Tokens are auto-saved to collection variables.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["const r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', r.token);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"email\":\"admin@example.com\",\"password\":\"admin123\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Employee)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["const r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('employeeToken', r.token);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"email\":\"employee@test.com\",\"password\":\"secret123\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Manager)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["const r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('managerToken', r.token);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"email\":\"manager@test.com\",\"password\":\"secret123\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Finance)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["const r = pm.response.json(); if (r.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('financeToken', r.token);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"email\":\"finance@test.com\",\"password\":\"secret123\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me / Validate Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/auth/me", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["auth", "me"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Users",
      "description": "ADMIN only. Create and list users.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List All Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/users", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["users"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create User (any role)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\",\n  \"role\": \"EMPLOYEE\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/users", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["users"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create User (invalid — expect 400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"X\",\n  \"email\": \"not-an-email\",\n  \"password\": \"12\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/users", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["users"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create User (duplicate — expect 409)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Dup\",\n  \"email\": \"employee@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/users", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["users"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Users (EMPLOYEE — expect 403)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/users", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["users"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Categories",
      "description": "ADMIN only. Create, update, and list categories.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Categories",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/categories", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["categories"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Category",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["const r = pm.response.json(); if (r.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId', r.id);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"name\":\"Transporte\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/categories", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["categories"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Rename Category",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"name\":\"Transporte — atualizado\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/categories/{{categoryId}}", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["categories", "{{categoryId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Deactivate Category",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"active\":false}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/categories/{{categoryId}}", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["categories", "{{categoryId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Category (EMPLOYEE — expect 403)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"name\":\"Hacked\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/categories", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["categories"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Reimbursements — Full Cycle",
      "description": "1. Employee creates → 2. Submits → 3. Manager approves → 4. Finance pays",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Create (Employee)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": ["const r = pm.response.json(); if (r.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('reimbursementId', r.id);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"description\": \"Lunch with client\",\n  \"amount\": 85.50,\n  \"expenseDate\": \"2026-04-25\",\n  \"categoryId\": \"{{categoryId}}\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Submit (Employee)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/submit", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "submit"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Approve (Manager)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{managerToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/approve", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "approve"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Pay (Finance)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{financeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/pay", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "pay"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Reimbursements — Other Actions",
      "description": "List, detail, reject, cancel, history.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List (Employee — sees own)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List (Manager — sees SUBMITTED)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{managerToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List (Finance — sees APPROVED)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{financeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List (Admin — sees all)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Edit (DRAFT only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"description\": \"Lunch — updated\",\n  \"amount\": 95.00\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject (Manager — requires reason)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{managerToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\"rejectionReason\":\"Amount exceeds policy limit\"}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/reject", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "reject"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel (Employee)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/cancel", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "cancel"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/history", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "history"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Pay Rejected (FINANCE — expect 400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{financeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/pay", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "pay"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Attachments",
      "description": "Upload and list attachments on a reimbursement.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Attachment (PDF)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"fileName\": \"receipt.pdf\",\n  \"fileUrl\": \"https://example.com/receipt.pdf\",\n  \"fileType\": \"application/pdf\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/attachments", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "attachments"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Upload Attachment (JPG)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"fileName\": \"photo.jpg\",\n  \"fileUrl\": \"https://example.com/photo.jpg\",\n  \"fileType\": \"image/jpeg\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/attachments", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "attachments"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Upload (invalid type — expect 400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"fileName\": \"virus.exe\",\n  \"fileUrl\": \"https://example.com/v.exe\",\n  \"fileType\": \"application/x-msdos-program\"\n}", "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } } },
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/attachments", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "attachments"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Attachments",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{employeeToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{url}}/reimbursements/{{reimbursementId}}/attachments", "host": ["{{url}}"], "path": ["reimbursements", "{{reimbursementId}}", "attachments"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "url", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "employeeToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "managerToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "financeToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "reimbursementId", "value": "" }
  ]
}
